LIFT & LIGHTEN EYE SERUM

New larger size, same price.

•Includes hyaluronic acid crosslinked, ceramides, and jujube extract for increased moisturizing and collagen building.

•This legendary sunny yellow lotion-serum lifts, brightens. smoothes in lines and sagging tissue, moisturizes and helps build collagen all in one product.  With continued regular use twice a day, pigmentation deposits around the eye area fade, leaving the eyes brighter and younger and more rested looking. 

•Avocado oil contains high amounts of Vitamin A, B1, B2, D, and E and works to smooth the thin skin around the eye.  Avocado extract firms and plumps lines and wrinkles around the eye area.

•Cucumber seed oil contains 3 main fatty acids, phytosterols, natural tocopherols and minerals. Phytosterols help the skin strengthen its lipid barrier, restoring proper moisture balance, smoothing the skins surface, improving skin elasticity and nourish and stimulate the skin cells to encourage regeneration of healthy skin cells.

•Chrysin and vitamin K act upon some of the causes of darkening around the eyes. Allergies, food intolerances, lack of sleep and dehydration are other causes worth eliminating. 

•Eyebright and cucumber extracts tone the undereye tissues and help to reduce puffiness. Sleeping on the back, reducing salt intake and doing Tanaka massage can also help.

•Lecithin and d-panthenol help to rebuild and protect tissues. Lecithin helps with penetration of the active ingredients into the tissues. 

•Contains light refracting spheres to minimize appearance of fine lines.

INGREDIENTS: Aqua, hyaluronic acid crosslinked, vitamin K , chrysin, pure glacier hydrosol, natural bisabolol, glycerin (vegetable source), ceramides, Zizyphus Jujuba Seed Extract, olive leaf extract, 1-3 beta glucans, Sea L'Silk™, biotin, organic avocado oil, avocado extract, organic cucumber seed oil,  tocopherol, caviar extract, polysaccharides, eyebright extract, d-panthenol, lecithin, chitin, cucumber extract, organic mint essential oil, hydrospheres, PrettyFace® flower essence, phenoxyethanol as preservative.  

USAGE:  Do not apply to upper eyelids as it may cause stinging in some people. Apply twice a day by massaging and pressing a very small amount around each eye avoiding the upper eyelid.  Should be used on the undereye and crowsfeet areas, extending to temples and brows.

•Vitamin K may cause transient stinging sensation, please do a patch test first on another part of the body. Gently pat the serum upward along the bony rim of the eye and brow bone to lift the area.  Use on freshly cleansed and slightly damp skin to seal in moisture then follow with serum or moisturizer of choice and sunscreen daily.

•As with any product you have never used before, do a patch test before applying to your face and discontinue use if irritation occurs, Please see "About MyFawnie" for instructions for patch test.

20 grams in airless pump bottle. $45

