PHOTOSHOP: Collagen Firming and Line-Blurring Cream
30g airless pump jar/$50

•A lightweight and highly emollient sheer apricot colored and apricot scented cream for mature skin that blurs lines and wrinkles visibly while firming and stimulating it to behave like younger skin. Hydrolyzed collagen, hyaluronic acid, and amino acids contribute to the skin's moisture levels and health.

•Does not contain retinol.

•Soft focus spheres fill in tiny lines and blur the edges of wrinkles by refracting light rather than covering up skin like a concealer would do.

•Colloidal gold gives a glow and refracts light.

•Dipalmitoyl hydroxyproline tightens and energizes cells to stimulate collagen production.

•Contains barrier-repairing and protecting ingredients: ceramides, cholesterol, fatty acids and phosphosphingolipids. Improves skin's elasticity and moisture levels.

•Pomegranate seed oil and extract promote keratinocyte production and inhibit MMP-1 production, promoting regeneration of the dermis and epidermis. http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16221534

•To be massaged into the skin in upward and outward strokes for lifting and tightening effects while imparting moisture and suppleness to the tissues. May be used anywhere that special care is needed for lifting, firming and blurring of lines. Play with it! Use it on bare skin, over sunscreen, or over makeup!

• May be used as a primer for makeup. Allow a few minutes for it to tighten the skin and fill in lines before applying anything over it.

•May have a slight warming or stinging sensation as it tightens and stimulates the skin. **Exercise caution using it around the eye area ** and flush eyes copiously with clean water if stinging occurs. Discontinue use if irritation occurs.

•Can also be used on lips for visible and tangible plumping and smoothing.

INGREDIENTS: Pure glacier water,  Hawaiian algae extract, dipalmitoyl hydroxyproline, organic French plum oil, organic pomegranate seed oil and pomegranate extract, hydrolyzed collagen, biotin, ceramide/cholesterol/phosphosphingolipids, mixed tocopherols, glycine, trehalose, glycerin, proprietary minerals complex, schizandra extract, hyaluronic acid, cellulose spheres, nylon-12, serine, pullulan, oat beta glucans, lecithin, Sea L'Silk™, natural bisabolol, p-anisic acid, colloidal gold, CO2 extracted organic rosehip seed oil, organic rosewood oil.

