KIN-NIA-NAG SERUM:
For all skin types.

•This serum is based upon SEA's revolutionary formula for revitalizing the skin.

•Does not contain retinol. If you need a retinol serum, please order Blue Heaven serum on this website.

•Kinetin,  Niacinamide, and N-Acetyl-Glucosamine promote collagen production and lighten skin hyperpigmentation in a safe and natural way that is compatible with all skin types including oily, normal, dry and mature. Especially good for blemish prone skin as niacinamide is proven to be healing and blemish-discouraging.

•Biotin is an essential B vitamin and acts in synergy with niacinamide and N-acetyl glucosamine for skin health.

•Lightweight gel-cream suitable for day and/or night use. Softens skin perfectly without stickiness and promotes collagen production.  Imparts a cooling sensation. pH 5.5

INGREDS: Aqua, 0.1% kinetin, niacinamide,  N-acetyl glucosamine, biotin, pure organic passionfruit oil, pure organic French Plum Oil, lecithin, trehalose (non-oily moisture binder), d-panthenol, L-carnosine, natural bisabolol (antioxidant, anti-inflammatory and penetration enhancer), Hawaiian algae extract, sclerotium gum, xanthan, pullulan, vitamin E acetate, natural preservative, organic wild mint essential oil (natural penetration enhancer).

USAGE:  Apply to freshly cleansed skin once or twice daily. May be used morning and/or night. This is the little sister to Holy Grail and is more suitable for younger skin than Holy Grail. 

As with any product you have never used before, do a patch test before applying to your face. Please see "About MyFawnie" for instructions for patch test.

30 ml bottle/$40


