A.C.E. OIL FOR DERMAROLLING:

15ml cobalt blue glass dropper bottle/$20

Contains: 
•1.0% Encapsulated Retinol (vitamin A) 

•Tetrahexyldecyl Ascorbate (oil soluble non irritating non-acid vitamin C) 

•Tocopherols alpha, beta, gamma and delta (vitamin E) 

•Passionfruit seed (Maracuja) oil which is known for its content of Piceatannol, essential fatty acids, and vitamin C.  Piceatannol is a potent sirtuin activator (more so than resveratrol).

•Pomegranate Seed OIl stimulates keratinocytes in the skin.
Rosemary Antioxidant to inhibit oxidation of the oils. 

Usage:
After dermarolling, apply A.C.E. Oil in the evening for the first 5 days and Stable Double C Serum in the daytime; 

May also be used to prepare skin for 6 weeks before dermarolling as it contains vitamin C and retinol. May be used all over the body.

