UNDERWEAR SERUM

•For all skin types and shades. Protects skin from oxidative stress under sunscreen.

•To be used under sunscreen each morning. May also be used at night under Holy Grail or Blue Heaven or KNN for additional skin lightening/clarifying effects. 

•Contains red and brown algae extracts, chlorella and antioxidants in a light tan oil-free serum base to mop up and absorb any UV light that may get thru your sunscreen.

•Shake well before each use. Keep in dark cool place but does not need refrigeration.

•Also contains skin lightening/clarifying extracts of bearberry, mulberry, kojic acid, liquorice and burnet. Does not contain hydroquinone.

"UV-absorbing substance in the red alga Porphyra yezoensis (Bangiales, Rhodophyta) block thymine photodimer production."
