INGREDIENTS:
Aqua, ferulic acid, chlorella, morus alba root extract, glycyrrhiza glabra root extract, poterium sanguisorba root extract, uva ursi leaf extract, kojic acid, red algae extract, brown algae extract, silymarin, hyaluronic acid, orchid extract (skin soother and barrier repair), emblica (Indian gooseberry) extract, hydroxyethylcellulose, vitamin E acetate, watercress extract, vitamin B3, zinc PCA, natural preservative, Glycerin, lecithin.  

30 ml airless pump bottle $40

